cast.original_title: To All the Boys: Always and Forever
cast.overview: Senior year of high school takes center stage as Lara Jean returns from a family trip to Korea and considers her college plans — with and without Peter.
cast.title: To All the Boys: Always and Forever

details.biography: Kayla Deorksen, (the O is silent...), is a Vancouver based actor, working in film, TV and theatre. After graduating from the National Theatre School of Canada, she returned to the West Coast where she's been working professionally ever since. When not acting she can be found running on the sea-wall or drinking Americanos at the local Catfé.
details.name: Kayla Deorksen
